體？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"economic entity呢,我自己覺得實體唔係蝗語"},{"pid":"a94aec450e719b89480f46b18a0f7a0b63bcd1bf","tid":2446592,"uid":71657,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:41:38.000Z","msg":"所有以前無 而家有嘅詞都話係蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔諗下其實係而家同以前唔同，多咗好多新事物所以先有新詞語出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa9b3fdc04f09d0177d65cfe88393b27ef4ec04","tid":2446592,"uid":266892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b71be567315508cb3b3a1c1496c4fe3f30869eef","tid":2446592,"uid":39253,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"495cb0d21dc17090f888e6f02863feec44faa38b","tid":2446592,"uid":266892,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c0adeb6cff9515e0b1ffb6bc9cd1a45edd47fdb","tid":2446592,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T14:59:03.000Z","msg":"Yes, how?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:13:01.000Z","msg":"（獨立）個體？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:40:31.000Z","msg":"economic entity呢,我自己覺得實體唔係蝗語"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T15:54:34.000Z","msg":"的確唔係 不過我覺得將entity譯做實體有啲唔準確<br />\n<br />\n實體既實字 應該係虛實既實 tangible之類既意思<br />\n<br />\n而entity係劍橋同朗文詞典既定義分別係<br />\n<br />\nsomething that exists apart from other things, having its own independent existence<br />\n<br />\n同埋<br />\n<br />\nsomething that exists as a single and complete unit<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得叫（獨立）個體會準確啲 （雖則individual都譯做個體）"}]}